OL,6,FDue to it's construction with
OL,7,Fsandstone a specialist cleaning team
OL,8,Fwill now be needed to fix the damage.
OL,10,FIt comes just a day before a wedding
OL,11,Fwas due to take place at St James
OL,12,FChurch on Saturday. Now, locals and
OL,13,Fmembers of the congregation are coming
OL,14,Ftogether to make sure it's ready.
OL,16,FThe Revd Wolverson said: "One
OL,17,Fencouraging note is the way I've had
OL,18,Fendless offers of help and support
OL,19,Ffrom the community and the local
OL,20,Fcouncil, neighbours, friends, and
OL,21,Fmembers of the congregation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
