OL,6,F"The Community has really rallied."
OL,8,FDet Sgt Lee Jamieson, of Lancashire
OL,9,FPolice, said: "This is a disgraceful
OL,10,Fact of vandalism which shows a
OL,11,Fcomplete lack of respect and which has
OL,12,Fleft the church and its parishioners
OL,13,Funderstandably extremely upset,
OL,14,Fespecially given the time of year.
OL,16,F"We are taking this matter incredibly
OL,17,Fseriously and this is being treated as
OL,18,Fa hate crime.
