OL,6,F"We do not tolerate hate of any form,
OL,7,Fand we will do everything in our power
OL,8,Fto identify the offenders and take the
OL,9,Fappropriate action.
OL,11,F"I would urge anyone in the community
OL,12,Fwho has any information which could
OL,13,Fhelp us identify who has done this to
OL,14,Fcome forward and speak to us."
OL,16,FYou can contact us on 101 quoting log
OL,17,F0399 of April 18th.
OL,19,FAlternatively contact independent
OL,20,Fcharity Crimestoppers on 0800 555 111
